#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_versions/2.2/guides/datasource.adoc:132
msgid "The database kind defines which type of database you will connect to."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_versions/2.2/guides/datasource.adoc:134
msgid "We currently include these built-in database kinds:"
